      "content": "The term \"fake news\" is often weaponized as a catch-all dismissal to delegitimize opposing viewpoints rather than accurately describe the phenomenon. While it signals deliberate falsehoods, it's frequently used as a rhetorical weapon to shut down legitimate criticism of a political side. A more accurate approach is to focus on the systemic spread of disinformation and propaganda, which is a much broader and more complex issue.",
      "source": "target",
